title: ASICS Tiger GEL-Kayano 5 KZN
details: Product #: 1A408001A Turn of the Century Classic, RebornThe ’90s were a time of excellent films, entertainment, and fashion. And when it came to creating the ASICS Men's Tiger GEL-Kayano 5 KZN, the sneaker profiles from that decade served to inspire. The thick sole allows for a large amount of gel cushioning, making the shoe an ideal cross-trainer or everyday sneaker for anyone looking for something hip and different with a whole lot of comfort.  Born to Cushion and PerformThe upper of these shoes is sturdy synthetic mixed with mesh panels to keep your feet dry all day, every day, from working out at the gym to running errands around town. The sturdy, broad design ensures that you're supported from all angles, while the innovative TRUSSTIC technology keeps the outsole protected so your shoe won't twist up on you when least expected. ASICS Men's Tiger GEL-Kayano 5 KZN features:• Classic ’90s Asics silhouette provides throwback style.• Synthetic leather and mesh upper provides a durable, ventilated feel for your feet.• Classic tiger stripe branding and overlays add to visual appeal.• Super soft GEL® technology keeps feet cushioned and supported all day. • Visible cutout of GEL at outsole adds a pop of color.• Textured rubber outsole provides excellent traction.

title: ASICS Tiger Modern OG Track Jacket
details: Product #: A078001 The Track Has Your Back The Modern Track Jacket by Asics not only boasts a head-turning design, but will deliver the perfect balance of comfort and mobility. Ideal as a layering piece in and out of the gym, the full-zip front allows you to shield against the cold or potential wind resistance. Also featuring trendy branding detail, show the world that fashion need not sacrifice function. From hem to pockets, this is the only track jacket you'll need. Athletic Functional Fashion This Asics Jacket is advanced in it's functions due to carefully applied ventilation and moisture-wicking fibers. Whether your movement of choice takes place in the gym or on the trails, this garment is crafted for mobility. Never again will you face the choice of free movement versus comfort. Now you have both. Just like you, there's now a modern jacket that is equally soft and tough for whatever challenges are thrown it's way. Asics Modern Track Jacket Features: • Reflective branding enhances aesthetic of retro style.• Relaxed fit provides freedom of movement.• Quick drying fabrics for comfort during active engagement.• Main Material: 100% polyester. Imported.
